Well I had the theory about CHA having a huge effect on Charm in the theories section, mostly because thats what all the charm fanatics say.  Personally I am a strong int believer.<P>With the mana pool thing, again that another one of those things several high level enchanters claim, along with the fact that all that extra mana only has a real effect when you are full on mana.  Course its nothing but theories and really depends upon playing style.<P>Tsunamii thank you for putting in your input into this.<P>Boy it would be nice if more people replied to this, so people creating characters can get lots of info.
